des: WOLD is your local hometown radio station playing all of your favorites from the 60's, 70's, 80's and Beyond! Our music is the perfect soundtrack for anything, anytime! In fact, we're confident it's SO good, that you'll want to keep listening so you don't miss a single song and the memories they bring back. Playing your favorites is our goal each and every day at WOLD, Your Music & Information Station, Now proud to serve Philadelphia, New York City and the world at WOLDradio.com
